  "prompt": "Which place serves the best coffee in New Delhi?",
  "response": "Finding the best coffee in New Delhi can be subjective, as it depends on personal preferences. However, some popular and highly-regarded places known for their coffee include:\n\n1. **Indian Coffee House:** Known for its vintage charm and classic coffee.\n2. **Blue Tokai Coffee Roasters:** Celebrated for its artisanal coffee made from freshly roasted beans sourced from Indian coffee estates.\n3. **Perch Wine and Coffee Bar:** Offers a sophisticated setting with a focus on high-quality coffee and a comfortable ambiance.\n4. **Third Wave Coffee Roasters:** Known for its specialty coffee, offering a variety of single-origin brews.\n5. **Di Ghent Caf\u00e9:** Combines Belgian flavors with freshly brewed coffee in a cozy environment.\n\nIt\u2019s recommended to visit these places and find your personal favorite. Each caf\u00e9 has its unique ambiance and coffee flavors, contributing to the rich coffee culture in New Delhi.",
